illam, Arathy and Ramljak, Marco and Reader, Arran T. and Reed, W. Robert and R{\"o}er, Jan Philipp and Ropovik, Ivan and Savi, Alexander O. and Schmidt, Kathleen and Schnabel, Landon and Sevigny, Eric L. and Shaki, Samuel and Shakya, Shishir and Soh, Andrew and Somo, Angela and Sonmez, Fatih and Str{\o}mland, Eirik and Suchow, Jordan W. and Szabelska, Anna and Tagat, Anirudh and Tutor, Melba Verra and Urbanska, Karolina and Van Dessel, Pieter and Vargo, Elisabeth Julie and Vo, Diem Thi Hong and Volkman, Victor and Wang, Ke and Wichman, Aaron L. and Williams, Jamal R. and Winter, Fabian and Wintermantel, Ferdinand and Zhang, Nan and Ziano, Ignazio and Zogmaister, Cristina and Zupan, Zorana and Nosek, Brian A. and Errington, Timothy M.},
  year = 2026,
